Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗中 他的脸微微泛着白光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那好像捕获了夜空所有星光的瞳眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 "永远"是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我依旧能够想起当时只有17岁的他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次联谊的女孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这个周末我们要见个面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一对一见面总有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是对方女孩子觉得害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她问我能不能带朋友来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你能跟我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人去吧 好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦 求求你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半天就行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗? 我们是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫其他人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你其他人都没空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天1点半站前广场见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 星期天你要穿哪件外套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不穿运动服的话 我就穿红色的那件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那件啊 和我的很像的那件?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果同时穿的话很像情侣装 有点怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情侣装不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 你千万别穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次你们也见过面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先去喝点茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦 好无聊的 去逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天都是陪他们来的 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢吃辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你喜欢吃什么就点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 啊~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本不需要人来陪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联谊 竹内一直坐在右边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坐在左边第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实对联谊没有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你还记得我的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真的抱歉 我不擅长记别人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我给人的印象一向都不突出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知纱很可爱的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 上回联谊 你还是人气第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对我来说 你才是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 算你诚实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是败给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人气第一名怎么会沦为电灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还是只能跟自己喜欢上的人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内 你有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会连自己害怕的联谊都会硬着头皮参加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 转换心情其实也很难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是你喜欢的地方 哪里都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么单独见面会害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别理他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到那坐公交车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 路上小心 宫田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我骗了你 一切都是我让他们演出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想再见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次完全没机会跟你讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天见了面 说了话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然和我想得一样 是个非常好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你说了谎 骗了你 真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道竹内不习惯这种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我能和你再见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一个月就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能给我机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊 拉拉 别压着我 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉美 拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 七美 好重 不要压着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fad(500,0)\1c&H1B3DFC&\3c&H01BCFA&}晴\N朗\N的\N星\N期\N日\N早\N晨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一大早在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天借一下你的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要开庆祝会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内的第一任女友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有女生对阿竹说 只要一个月就好 能给我机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他不好意思拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拉拉炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过附带期限的交往也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不交往看看 怎么知道合不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天我有约会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就穿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,370)\frz12\1c&H1B3DFC&\3c&H01BCFA&}红\N色\N运\N动\N外\N套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是故意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天我再三叮嘱 你却...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的话你一句也听不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门前急急忙忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还找什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像上次那样我可不会上当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是穿上衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\1c&H9B84FB&}宠物世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱 好可爱 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我家的拉拉美最可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高基犬耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边还有松鼠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我要拍下来做待机画面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很充实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想养高基犬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫也很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是我家拉拉美最可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会喜欢上一个你对他没感觉的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 明明不喜欢还交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后强迫自己喜欢上对方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是喜欢过原本讨厌的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌过我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高一的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在为什么还问这个 难道以前没发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌也是喜欢的一种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为在意所以才会产生讨厌的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野以前也说过这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这种事总是很难如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大红色的情侣装
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然真有这么穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是分开走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 丑女说的话别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如 男朋友很白痴 很想扁他一顿的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑容太可爱 不知不觉就原谅他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次 我都被自己的心情打败
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的心情往往跟努力的方向相反
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会对他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 小七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\1c&H06ADEC&}小水小高版的"我们也存在"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱到来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水口叶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终回到底在哪呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢 被喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠绵的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情快点来到我身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由请水口叶演唱一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on My love
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on my love
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子摘掉眼镜后就表示恋爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很容易分辨呢 不过对象是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐形眼镜 不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有习惯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰尘很容易进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛红得像兔子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是戴眼镜比较适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再拿个球来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不试着交往看看 不会明白合不合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往一个月后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行 还是无法喜欢上你 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如一开始就拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月之前 和交往一个月之后 结果都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我就有心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不喜欢还和别人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是义务劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是为了慢慢喜欢上她才去交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会喜欢上她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真斩钉截铁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是从来都没喜欢上过喜欢你的女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我会试着去喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和不喜欢的女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:15:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何不把你的女人弄哭才是当务之急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在帮他设计发型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是金秋最酷的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再梳过去一点就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从左边整个梳过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不对称的好看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是矢野的头发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你掉头发很严重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内 你流血了 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你舔舔消消毒 就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没在打架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元 刚才我话说重了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一直都是我话说的过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不能停滞不前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菅野美穗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菅野?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皮肤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:17:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你的作业带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天在学校也可以给我的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地那么晚送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有肉包子 夜宵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包子?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说竹内有女朋友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不替他高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可不好 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这么做不像他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 努力一下也许会喜欢上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊 奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内 其实想和自己喜欢的女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 他真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩一定能够了解竹内的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发湿漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为傍晚刚洗过澡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你里面是睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借你毛衣穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 你会感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿了很多 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我帮你暖身子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 有人会经过的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害羞啦 不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然没穿胸罩...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你带头巾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止头部受寒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小红帽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想和高桥去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 不能着急
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不是指那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去一个地方 两人能够独处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人打扰的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用急着当天回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用急着分开的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想快点长大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大了 把高桥抢到手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有"永远"的话该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的哦 一定有的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗中 他的脸微微泛着白光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那好像捕获了夜空所有星光的瞳眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 "永远"是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我依旧能够想起当时只有17岁的他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大之后的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚的知道"永远"并不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不再是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间停止 世界仿佛只剩下我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个瞬间 无比真实 却又无比梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有一瞬 却能感受到了"永远"的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在年轻如我们的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.24,0:22:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然坚信 "永远"是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我看到短信了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:22:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天车站前见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终会长大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.69,0:25:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六晚上 你到我家来住一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.00,0:25:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人可以整天在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.61,0:25:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本的母亲病倒了 现在我们在医院
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.38,0:25:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...山本...要选今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.59,0:25:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.47,0:25:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.57,0:25:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎收看下集

